This plugin is an independent reimplementation of the launch-options
management functionality popularised by the decky-launch-options
Decky-Loader plugin:

  https://github.com/Wurielle/decky-launch-options
  Copyright (c) Wurielle (MIT) / Steam Deck Homebrew (BSD-3-Clause)

No source code from decky-launch-options was copied or transliterated.
This plugin reads and writes Steam's `localconfig.vdf` directly via the
in-tree `@loadout/vdf` package; the upstream is credited here for
inspiration and feature-parity reference only.
